# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# ATTESTA — Environment Variables
# Copy to .env and fill in values.
# NEVER commit .env to git.
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────
# PostgreSQL 16 (Docker: localhost:5432)
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://attesta:attesta_dev@localhost:5432/attesta"

# ── Cache / Queue ─────────────────────────
# Redis 7 (Docker: localhost:6379)
REDIS_URL="redis://localhost:6379"

# ── Next.js Web App ───────────────────────
NEXTAUTH_URL="http://localhost:3000"
# Generate: openssl rand -base64 32
NEXTAUTH_SECRET="replace-me-openssl-rand-base64-32"

# ── OAuth Providers ───────────────────────
# Google: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=""
GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=""

# GitHub: https://github.com/settings/developers
GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=""
GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=""

# ── Email (Resend) ────────────────────────
# https://resend.com — magic link / OTP auth
RESEND_API_KEY=""
EMAIL_FROM="no-reply@attesta.io"

# ── Privy.io (Embedded Wallets) ───────────
# https://console.privy.io
# Silently creates a Polygon wallet for every new user
NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIVY_APP_ID=""
PRIVY_APP_SECRET=""

# ── Fastify API ───────────────────────────
API_PORT=4000
# Generate: openssl rand -base64 64
JWT_ACCESS_SECRET="replace-me-64-chars"
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET="replace-me-64-chars-different"
# httpOnly cookie settings
COOKIE_SECRET="replace-me-32-chars"
# Comma-separated allowed origins
CORS_ORIGINS="http://localhost:3000"

# ── Environment ───────────────────────────
NODE_ENV="development"
